title: F.E.X Forced Evolution Experiment-PLAZA
description:
F.E.X (Forced Evolution Experiment) (c) NonFictional Games

Release Date: 08/2017 Protection: Steam
Discs: 1 Genre: Action

In F.E.X (Forced Evolution Experiment) you are a failed experiment
in a facility where they manipulate human DNA in order to stop the
aging process. Something happens in the facility and you manage to
escape, but as a failed experiment you are able to grow old at will
but you can't reverse the process. Get out of the lab before you die
of age or get caught by other experiments

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/655700/

1. Extract release
2. Mount ISO
3. Install the game
4. Copy crack from the PLAZA folder
5. Play!
